67
00:05:18,324 --> 00:05:20,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His opponent is the God Foot,</b></font>

68
00:05:20,264 --> 00:05:23,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the man they say has a superhuman
