84
00:06:40,944 --> 00:06:42,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A combined stage?</b></font>

85
00:06:42,614 --> 00:06:46,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. One race, both hillclimb and downhill.</b></font>

86
00:06:46,354 --> 00:06:49,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll repeat that until the winner's decided.</b></font>

87
00:06:55,854 --> 00:06:57,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speaking of Kozo Hoshino,</b></font>

88
00:06:57,664 --> 00:06:59,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>my most lasting impression of him</b></font>

89
00:06:59,794 --> 00:07:03,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is from when he was still driving an R32.</b></font>

90
00:07:03,664 --> 00:07:05,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was at a going-away party,</b></font>

91
00:07:05,534 --> 00:07:08,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and Hoshino was at the last
corner of the Tsukuba circuit.</b></font>

92
00:07:08,704 --> 00:07:13,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw him drift the entire thing,
from entry to exit.</b></font>

93
00:07:13,544 --> 00:07:17,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can still see it, like it's
burned onto my retinas.</b></font>

94
00:07:18,784 --> 00:07:23,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The GTR's ATTESA E-TS
4WD system is a bit unusual</b></font>

95
00:07:23,224 --> 00:07:25,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and as a rule doesn't allow for drifting.</b></font>

96
00:07:25,824 --> 00:07:29,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's because if the E-TS detects tailslide,</b></font>

97
00:07:29,794 --> 00:07:33,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it simultaneously initiates front-wheel drive.</b></font>

98
00:07:33,034 --> 00:07:38,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so? I don't know that much about 4WD.</b></font>

99
00:07:38,164 --> 00:07:42,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In other words, even if you reduce
countersteer and step fully on the gas,</b></font>

100
00:07:42,204 --> 00:07:47,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can't maintain the slide angle
like in a normal rear-wheel drive.</b></font>

101
00:07:47,574 --> 00:07:54,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Front-side traction is increased,
and the car cancels out the drift.</b></font>

102
00:07:54,484 --> 00:07:58,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also, because ATTESA E-TS
is designed to assign torque</b></font>

103
00:07:58,984 --> 00:08:03,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to the front wheels automatically
according to acceleration,</b></font>

104
00:08:03,094 --> 00:08:05,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the more intricate your accelerator handling,</b></font>

105
00:08:05,764 --> 00:08:08,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the more difficult it becomes to sustain drift.</b></font>

106
00:08:08,894 --> 00:08:12,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you said his GT-R was drifting, right?</b></font>

107
00:08:12,764 --> 00:08:18,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drifting flawlessly.
Even Mr. Toudou was shocked by it.</b></font>

108
00:08:18,404 --> 00:08:21,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He said he had no explanation
for that kind of technique.</b></font>

109
00:08:21,874 --> 00:08:24,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Mr. Toudou said that?</b></font>

110
00:08:24,714 --> 00:08:27,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unthinkable, is it?</b></font>

111
00:08:27,014 --> 00:08:31,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, to Hoshino it was probably
a little game, just him showing off.</b></font>

112
00:08:31,924 --> 00:08:36,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if that's why Mr. Toudou
said we should come watch this race.</b></font>

113
00:08:36,794 --> 00:08:43,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. No doubt about it, Hoshino
has godlike mastery of pedal work.</b></font>

114
00:08:43,104 --> 00:08:47,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why they call him the God Foot.</b></font>

115
00:08:47,604 --> 00:08:50,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, Mr. Toudou
also said something else...</b></font>

116
00:08:50,474 --> 00:08:56,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That we should watch how Project D
faces the giant wall before them.</b></font>

117
00:08:56,614 --> 00:08:58,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What kind of race will this turn out to be?</b></font>

118
00:08:58,744 --> 00:09:01,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't wait to find out.</b></font>

119
00:09:10,094 --> 00:09:14,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the GT-R line alone,
I've gone through R32, 33 and 34...</b></font>

120
00:09:14,064 --> 00:09:20,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four cars already. The R32 had such
an impact on me when it debuted!</b></font>

121
00:09:22,274 --> 00:09:27,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But when the bigger R33 came out,
talk about a disappointment.</b></font>

122
00:09:27,574 --> 00:09:31,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That one pretty much sucked! One, two...</b></font>

123
00:09:31,114 --> 00:09:32,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hyaa!</b></font>

124
00:09:35,784 --> 00:09:41,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got rid of that R33 right quick
and bought another R32...</b></font>

125
00:09:41,294 --> 00:09:46,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...meaning that my fourth car
was this, the R34 GT-R!</b></font>

126
00:09:53,704 --> 00:09:55,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

127
00:09:55,834 --> 00:09:59,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's keepin' up with me, eh? Well done.</b></font>

128
00:10:03,214 --> 00:10:05,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's so damn fast!</i></b></font>

129
00:10:08,314 --> 00:10:12,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I was full of confidence after having</i>
<i>upped my car's racing capabilities...</i></b></font>

130
00:10:12,554 --> 00:10:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But I was naive.</i></b></font>

131
00:10:14,494 --> 00:10:18,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sure enough, when it comes to</i>
<i>traction, the GT-R is a monster!</i></b></font>

132
00:10:32,904 --> 00:10:36,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you ride in Mr. Hoshino's
