145
00:11:37,944 --> 00:11:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ko talks so that he doesn't</i>
<i>concentrate too much.</i></b></font>

146
00:11:43,044 --> 00:11:46,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's the type of guy who gets</i>
<i>more fired up than anyone!</i></b></font>

147
00:11:46,144 --> 00:11:51,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Put simply, it's a cooling</i>
<i>system for his emotions.</i></b></font>

148
00:11:51,054 --> 00:11:56,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is the method he thought of so that</i>
<i>he wouldn't lose his cool or his objectivity.</i></b></font>

149
00:12:00,264 --> 00:12:07,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I doubt it'll happen, but on</i>
<i>the off chance he stops talking...</i></b></font>

150
00:12:07,004 --> 00:12:10,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...then like a drag machine with</i>
<i>its nitrous system engaged,</i></b></font>

151
00:12:10,644 --> 00:12:13,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>he will race wild and unchecked!</i></b></font>

152
00:12:15,474 --> 00:12:17,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hyaaa!</b></font>

153
00:12:22,354 --> 00:12:28,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's the one thing I want to avoid.</i>
<i>Be sure to play this smart!</i></b></font>

154
00:12:28,824 --> 00:12:31,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>According to our age.</i></b></font>

155
00:12:31,824 --> 00:12:33,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Certainly is muggy tonight, isn't it?</b></font>

156
00:12:33,864 --> 00:12:36,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, if you'd care for one of these...</b></font>

157
00:12:40,604 --> 00:12:43,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Here.
--Thank you.</b></font>

158
00:12:44,174 --> 00:12:49,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you all right? You're really sweating.</b></font>

159
00:12:49,444 --> 00:12:53,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess I'm the age where heat hits you most.</b></font>

160
00:12:59,994 --> 00:13:03,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This R34 really is a great car!</b></font>

161
00:13:03,364 --> 00:13:09,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It even addresses the R32's one
weak point, stubborn understeer.</b></font>

162
00:13:09,194 --> 00:13:13,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It brakes well and it turns well.
There's no other car that's this fun!</b></font>

163
00:13:13,804 --> 00:13:17,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If someone's got a bit of money
and doesn't know anything about cars,</b></font>

164
00:13:17,244 --> 00:13:20,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he'll drive a Benz or a Ferrari or some crap.</b></font>

165
00:13:22,074 --> 00:13:27,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got money, but I couldn't care
less about those sorts of cars!</b></font>

166
00:13:27,554 --> 00:13:29,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Till the day I die...</b></font>

167
00:13:29,514 --> 00:13:31,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...give me a GT-R!</b></font>

168
00:13:43,704 --> 00:13:45,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hraa!</b></font>

169
00:13:48,774 --> 00:13:51,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Graa!</b></font>

170
00:14:05,954 --> 00:14:09,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Touge Tunnel Project</b></font>

171
00:14:05,954 --> 00:14:09,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}To be implemented soon"</b></font>

172
00:14:09,194 --> 00:14:16,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, you've never given Keisuke advice
the way that you did this time, have you?</b></font>

173
00:14:16,764 --> 00:14:20,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up till now, you've mostly let him act freely.</b></font>

174
00:14:20,204 --> 00:14:23,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That should be enough to tell you
our opponent this time is special.</b></font>

175
00:14:23,974 --> 00:14:26,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that, but...</b></font>

176
00:14:26,814 --> 00:14:30,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Under these rules, managing tire performance</b></font>

177
00:14:30,244 --> 00:14:33,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>during the hillclimb will be key.</b></font>

178
00:14:33,414 --> 00:14:37,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Relying on traction against
an opponent in a 4WD GT-R</b></font>

179
00:14:37,554 --> 00:14:40,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>would likely cause rapid tire deterioration.</b></font>

180
00:14:40,594 --> 00:14:46,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Keisuke has made dramatic progress
in his accelerator handling recently.</b></font>

181
00:14:46,634 --> 00:14:51,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That is my point. No matter how
much progress Keisuke has made,</b></font>

182
00:14:51,334 --> 00:14:54,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that skill will be of no use
against tonight's opponent.</b></font>

183
00:14:54,134 --> 00:14:57,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The man they call God Foot, eh?</b></font>

184
00:14:57,074 --> 00:15:00,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I had him restrain
himself for the hillclimb</b></font>

185
00:15:00,314 --> 00:15:02,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to wager the race on the downhill.</b></font>

186
00:15:02,014 --> 00:15:05,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, I understand that, but still...</b></font>

187
00:15:05,414 --> 00:15:08,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...isn't seven seconds a bit too dangerous?</b></font>

188
00:15:08,414 --> 00:15:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I heard that off to the side,
I shivered in spite of myself.</b></font>

189
00:15:11,324 --> 00:15:14,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I would say the odds of winning
hinge upon seven seconds.</b></font>

190
00:15:14,794 --> 00:15:18,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happens during those
seven seconds is most important.</b></font>

191
00:15:18,364 --> 00:15:24,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I am asking of Keisuke a race far
more difficult than any he has yet run.</b></font>

192
00:15:26,804 --> 00:15:31,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is a tactic that acknowledges his
progress in accelerator handling...</b></font>

193
00:15:31,774 --> 00:15:36,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And he probably understands my true intent.</b></font>

194
00:15:39,284 --> 00:15:43,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't believe you'd tell me</i>
<i>something like that, brother.</i></b></font>

195
00:15:43,154 --> 00:15:48,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Can we really take on a guy as fast as this</i>
<i>and give him a margin of seven seconds?</i></b></font>

196
00:15:48,954 --> 00:15:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I can't get that time back during</i>
<i>the downhill, it's game over!</i></b></font>

197
00:15:58,234 --> 00:16:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Keeping a margin may be hard, but in</i>
<i>terms of execution, anyone can do it!</i></b></font>

198
00:16:06,744 --> 00:16:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Still, my brother wouldn't bother saying</i>
<i>something that could be done that easily.</i></b></font>

199
00:16:12,884 --> 00:16:16,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The problem is...</i>
<i>what those seven seconds hold!</i></b></font>

200
00:16:20,254 --> 00:16:24,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not yet! No, not yet!</b></font>

201
00:16:27,664 --> 00:16:32,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My brother's probably asking</i>
<i>something incredibly difficult of me.</i></b></font>

202
00:16:32,404 --> 00:16:34,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to focus my body and spirit...</i></b></font>

203
00:16:34,274 --> 00:16:37,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...and concentrate on the</i>
<i>movement of my right foot.</i></b></font>

204
00:16:49,884 --> 00:16:51,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hyaa!</b></font>

205
00:16:57,364 --> 00:17:01,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah!
--Awesome! That's Hoshino for you!</b></font>

206
00:17:01,034 --> 00:17:03,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's slowly started to pull ahead of the FD!</b></font>

207
00:17:03,734 --> 00:17:08,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Jeez, I guess even Project D's
hillclimb ace is no big deal.</b></font>

208
00:17:08,274 --> 00:17:11,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Idiot, Hoshino is just too awesome.</b></font>

209
00:17:11,044 --> 00:17:14,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way an FD should be able to
keep up with an R34 on a course like this.</b></font>

210
00:17:14,774 --> 00:17:19,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this rate, Purple Shadow will win
both the hillclimb and the downhill!</b></font>

211
00:17:39,504 --> 00:17:44,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So that's your strategy, huh?
That's pretty clever of you.</b></font>

212
00:17:44,244 --> 00:17:46,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you're still young...</b></font>

213
00:17:46,174 --> 00:17:50,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you ask me, there's no need
for you to be that clever just yet.</b></font>

214
00:17:55,484 --> 00:18:00,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At his age, I was more of an idiot,
always on the offensive.</b></font>

215
00:18:01,694 --> 00:18:06,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, it's because of that I've been
able to come this far without losing.</b></font>

216
00:18:07,264 --> 00:18:09,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One, two!</b></font>

217
00:18:15,504 --> 00:18:20,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D's FD is slowly being left behind.</b></font>

218
00:18:20,514 --> 00:18:26,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How does this look to you, Sakai?
Will it all be over in the first race?</b></font>

219
00:18:26,784 --> 00:18:33,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not at all. It looks like this hillclimb
is using some nonstandard rules.</b></font>

220
00:18:33,024 --> 00:18:34,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nonstandard rules?</b></font>

221
00:18:34,554 --> 00:18:38,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The GT-R with its great traction
will have the uphill advantage,</b></font>

222
00:18:38,624 --> 00:18:42,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but on the downhill, the lightweight FD
could have the upper hand.</b></font>

223
00:18:42,894 --> 00:18:46,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So he might hold back on the hillclimb,
not placing wear on his tires</b></font>

224
00:18:46,234 --> 00:18:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>until the downhill, which he'll bet the race on.</b></font>

225
00:18:48,974 --> 00:18:51,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get it.</b></font>

226
00:18:51,374 --> 00:18:57,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait, so that means Project D is the one
that's actively trying to lay a trap?</b></font>

227
00:18:57,414 --> 00:19:00,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it's a big gamble, all or nothing.</b></font>

228
00:19:00,854 --> 00:19:05,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Trying this tactic on Kozo Hoshino
of all people will take some courage.</b></font>

229
00:19:05,754 --> 00:19:09,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he doesn't follow as predicted
on the downhill, it's all over.</b></font>

230
00:19:09,694 --> 00:19:10,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

231
00:19:10,764 --> 00:19:16,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's friggin' incredible how he
planned this... Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

232
00:19:16,034 --> 00:19:19,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The turnaround to the downhill
will be something to watch.</b></font>

233
00:19:19,034 --> 00:19:20,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kozo Hoshino and Keisuke Takahashi</b></font>

234
00:19:20,874 --> 00:19:24,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will engage in an all-out downhill race!</b></font>

235
00:19:24,104 --> 00:19:30,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're both probably well aware...
of where the importance of this race lies.</b></font>

236
00:19:30,284 --> 00:19:33,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just thinking about it is making me tingle.</b></font>

237
00:19:40,084 --> 00:19:42,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm prepared for the worst.</i></b></font>

238
00:19:42,024 --> 00:19:47,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All I can do is have my right foot</i>
<i>do the best possible job it can!</i></b></font>

239
00:19:47,294 --> 00:19:51,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If my brother says I can keep up</i>
<i>with him, I'll show them that I can!</i></b></font>

240
00:20:20,394 --> 00:20:22,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It won't be long.</b></font>

241
00:20:29,074 --> 00:20:34,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've got word from down below. It looks
like Keisuke is slowly being left behind.</b></font>

242
00:20:35,274 --> 00:20:40,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh. Well, the GT-R has the
advantage on the hillclimb.</b></font>

243
00:20:41,284 --> 00:20:46,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is probably a terrible feeling for Keisuke.</b></font>

244
00:20:46,484 --> 00:20:50,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he hasn't experienced this before.</b></font>

245
00:20:50,424 --> 00:20:56,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His opponent's car, disappearing without
a trace from his FD's windshield...</b></font>

246
00:21:06,204 --> 00:21:10,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Doing your best to control the frustration
at having your opponent disappear</b></font>

247
00:21:10,644 --> 00:21:16,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>while focusing all your concentration on the
tires' contact with the road is no easy task.</b></font>

248
00:21:16,714 --> 00:21:18,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said it...</b></font>

249
00:21:18,684 --> 00:21:21,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's all right! Keisuke can do it!</b></font>

250
00:21:23,394 --> 00:21:25,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to concentrate...</i></b></font>

251
00:21:25,624 --> 00:21:30,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Must keep horizontal gravity generated</i>
<i>from corner entry to exit steady.</i></b></font>

252
00:21:30,834 --> 00:21:33,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to control the tires' load!</i></b></font>

253
00:21:39,874 --> 00:21:43,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>At the corner exit, I'll open it up</i>
<i>full-throttle and make a dash for it!</i></b></font>

254
00:22:19,944 --> 00:22:23,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke fought his way through
races in the Saitama area</b></font>

255
00:22:23,514 --> 00:22:27,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with the aim of improving
his accelerator handling.</b></font>

256
00:22:27,054 --> 00:22:33,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As a result, he has seen vast improvement
in his management of tire performance.</b></font>

257
00:22:33,124 --> 00:22:37,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rapidity with which he has absorbed
these techniques has surprised even me.</b></font>

258
00:22:37,964 --> 00:22:42,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That is what makes Keisuke Takahashi
an extraordinary driver.</b></font>

259
00:22:42,034 --> 00:22:45,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If this race becomes protracted,</b></font>

260
00:22:45,044 --> 00:22:47,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the results of that experience should manifest.</b></font>

261
00:23:00,394 --> 00:23:02,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There they are!</b></font>

262
00:23:07,564 --> 00:23:09,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yo, there they are!</b></font>

263
00:23:09,964 --> 00:23:12,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's Hoshino's GT-R!</b></font>

264
00:23:12,134 --> 00:23:16,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's running all by himself!
This isn't a race at all!</b></font>

265
00:23:18,404 --> 00:23:20,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hyaa!</b></font>

266
00:23:22,014 --> 00:23:24,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hngraa!</b></font>

267
00:23:28,284 --> 00:23:30,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Awesome!
--So cool!</b></font>

268
00:23:36,094 --> 00:23:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't go lookin' down on my R34!</b></font>

269
00:24:09,694 --> 00:24:12,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go, Keisuke!</b></font>

270
00:24:18,634 --> 00:24:22,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello? Kenta? How many seconds was it?</b></font>

271
00:24:24,344 --> 00:24:26,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. Thanks.</b></font>

272
00:24:28,374 --> 00:24:31,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lag time at the turnaround
point was six seconds.</b></font>

273
00:24:31,884 --> 00:24:33,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

274
00:24:37,524 --> 00:24:40,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Well done, I suppose.</i></b></font>

275
00:24:40,024 --> 00:24:44,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He no doubt held back against</i>
<i>an opponent he couldn't see.</i></b></font>

276
00:24:44,524 --> 00:24:48,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Because now the real gamble begins.</i></b></font>

277
00:25:21,194 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Senjou ni saita rose,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

278
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mae ni shika susumenai caterpillar</i>
<i>ga kyou mo fumitsubushita</i></b></font>

279
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, nikushimi dake fuyashite</i></b></font>

280
00:25:33,374 --> 00:25:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, sonna sesou, live eizou</i></b></font>

281
00:25:37,484 --> 00:25:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dakishimete ite ne, motto tsuyoi te de</i></b></font>

282
00:25:46,224 --> 00:25:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Fuan na yoru ni anata no koe</i>
<i>(For the reason they don't know)</i></b></font>

283
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekai wa itsuka chi o nagashite ite</i>
<i>(All around the world)</i></b></font>

284
00:25:58,464 --> 00:26:08,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sonna news o wasuresasete yo, wakaritakunai</i></b></font>

285
00:26:09,574 --> 00:26:16,614
